						               													<description>You are a tour guide responsible for a group of 4 tourists that have travelled to the mysterious sites of Rocky Valley. Unfortunately, a landslide has forbidden your return home and you will have to stay for a few days. The only inn in town is the infamous Hostil Hostal, known for its intriguing past and deteriorating interior.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Your guests desperately need their rest but it will be hard to come by as you not only need to deal with the dangers of the hostel itself but also the insensitivity of the other guests.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Hostil Hostal is a strategic, entry level, family game. Players take turns placing guests in the beds of the different rooms of the inn. Each room brings different levels of comfort that will change according to its occupancy and deteriorating condition. Additionally, each guest&amp;rsquo;s rest will be affected by different events played in secret by each player. In the end, the player whose guests got the best sleep will be the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
